BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:mIkbmokoo5lvqaT5Ie9fe
SUMMARY:Summer Cannibals\, Divers\, LEMON BOY
DTSTAMP:20260327T062520Z
DTSTART:20260419T040000Z
DESCRIPTION:Advance: $15 ($20.09 after fees)\n\nDay of: $18 ($26.27 after f
	ees)\n\nSummer Cannibals:\n\nSummer Cannibals broke up. Three years later\
	, they made a new album. More on that later. In the meantime\, 2026 marks 
	the 10-year anniversary of their acclaimed third record\, Full Of It\, rel
	eased by NW punk mainstay Kill Rock Stars. To mark the anniversary\, the b
	and will play their first headlining shows since 2022\, performing the alb
	um front to back in Portland at Mississippi Studios and Seattle at Sunset 
	Tavern with longtime friends and Portland legends Divers.\n\nFull Of It\, 
	the album Pitchfork praised for “expertly balancing flame-belching Mad Max
	 riffage with lyrics frankly exploring questions of codependence and need\
	,” captured a turning point for the band\, sharpening their raw\, hook-dri
	ven sound into something more focused and intense. The anniversary is bein
	g marked with a vinyl repress\, two Northwest shows\, and a new album arri
